<h3>
To change your details or permissions</h3>
<p>You can at any time change the details we hold about you by logging into the website and updating your details under the ‘My Details’ tab of the members area. If you do not have an account, please contact us by the above methods.</p>
<p>If you have forgotten or do not know your password, please use your email address as your username and then follow the ‘Forgotten Password’ instructions.</p>
